latestPosts.caption:
The fabulous @maheepkapoor shared how being at #WeTheWomen Festival and having a conversation with @barkha.dutt was a truly special moment for her. The energy was electrifying, and the excitement was undeniable! ✨

 #WeTheWomen #MaheepKapoor #BollywoodWives #WTW2024

It’s okay to be weak, it’s okay to be vulnerable, and to surround yourself with people you love and trust,says Maheep Kapoor, offering an inspiring message for young people. Speaking at We The Women, she shared her insights during a panel that delved into the challenges and triumphs of being a woman. Reflecting on her journey and her experiences in the dazzling yet demanding world of Bollywood, @maheepkapoor highlighted how navigating such a world can often feel overwhelming but also rewarding.
